author: Morgan Phillips
title: 4 Michigan sheriffs say they won't strictly enforce Whitmer's stay-at-home order
description: Sheriffs from four different Michigan counties said Wednesday they will not strictly enforce Gov. Gretchen Whitmer’s social-distancing restrictions that critics say have gone too far.
